Introduction

HONEYZ is a six-member virtual group under the name Project [i].

The project group was announced on January 13, 2024, during a Honey Churros broadcast. On January 20 and 21, all the group members were announced during a live broadcast.

They debuted on August 30, 2024, with the single album Ready 2 Be Loved.

The fandom's name is a combination of the "Z" at the end of HONEYZ and the English word "Jelly."
